name: Nameless Venture V0.16 WEB
description:
"Nameless Venture" is a strategy game that is currently in development.

The game began to develop in early April 2020 during the global coronavirus quarantine. "

As the first objective from the game design is to be able to make a 2D version of the palm spacetrader.

Currently the game has 2 months of development and with the alpha version I aim to test the implemented mechanics and systems.

the music is the definitive, but

graphics are not final.

I thank you for trying the game.
